    "title": "Kuogopa Watu",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "kuogopa watu",
    "language": "swh",
    "content": "<p>Mungu anaahidi kuwa pamoja na watu wake wanapokutana na upinzani (tazama, kwa mfano, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut20:1-Deut20:4\">Kumbukumbu la Torati 20:1–4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh1:9\">Yoshua 1:9</a>). Mradi tu wanabaki waaminifu kwake, hawana sababu ya kuwaogopa wengine. Historia ya Israeli inaonyesha ukweli huu (tazama <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod14:10-Exod14:31\">Kutoka 14:10–31</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh10:9-Josh10:14\">Yoshua 10:9–14</a>). Hata hivyo, kwa wale wanaotafuta amani na usalama kwingineko, Mungu anaweza kuwa &quot;mwamba wa kukwaza&quot; badala ya &quot;patakatifu&quot; (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa8:14\">Isaya 8:14</a>).</p><p>Wakati wa utawala wa Mfalme Ahazi katika Yuda, alipatwa na hofu kubwa aliposikia kwamba Siria na Israeli walikuwa wameungana kupigana naye (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa7:2\">Isaya 7:2</a>). Bwana alimhimiza kuwa na imani, kwani imani ilikuwa muhimu kwa ulinzi wa Bwana (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa7:9\">7:9</a>). Hata hivyo, Ahazi aliamua kutomwamini Bwana. Badala yake, alitafuta msaada kutoka kwa Waashuri. Uamuzi huu ulimfanya Bwana kuwa &quot;mtego na tanzi&quot; kwake na kwa Israeli na Yuda yote (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa8:11-Isa8:15\">8:11–15</a>).</p><p>Ujumbe wa nabii Isaya ulikusudiwa kuonyesha tofauti kati ya imani na hofu. Mfalme Ahazi ni mfano wa hofu. Mfalme Hezekia ni mfano usio kamili wa imani (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa37:1-Isa37:38\">Isaya 37</a>). Isaya mwenyewe ni mfano bora wa imani (sura ya <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa8:1-Isa8:22\">8</a>). Hatimaye, &quot;Mtumishi&quot; wa Mungu ni mfano bora wa imani (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa42:1-Isa42:7\">42:1–7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa50:4-Isa50:7\">50:4–7</a>).</p><p>Yesu aliwaambia wafuasi wake wasiwaogope watu wanaowatishia, hata wale wanaotaka kuwaua (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt10:26-Matt10:31\">Mathayo 10:26–31</a>). Mungu anajua kila shomoro na idadi ya nywele ambazo ziko kwenye kichwa cha mtu. Mungu yupo pamoja na wale wanaomwamini. Wakristo wameonyesha imani hii katika historia kwa kutoogopa kile ambacho wengine wanaweza kuwafanyia, hata kufa kwa ajili ya imani yao (tazama <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts6:8-Acts7:60\">Matendo 6:8–7:60</a>).</p><p>Watu ambao hawajitolei kikamilifu kwa Mungu watawaogopa wengine. Lakini wale wanaomwamini Bwana wanaweza kushinda hofu hii. Wanatambua kwamba maadui wa kibinadamu ni wa muda, ilhali nguvu za Mungu hudumu milele.</p><p><u>Sehemu za Kujifunza Zaidi</u></p><p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num14:1-Num14:12\">Hesabu 14:1–12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num21:34-Num21:35\">21:34–35</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh1:9\">Yoshua 1:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs16:5-2Kgs16:18\">2 Wafalme 16:5–18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr28:16-2Chr28:23\">2 Mambo ya Nyakati 28:16–23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps23:4\">Zaburi 23:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov29:25\">Mithali 29:25</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa7:1-Isa7:25\">Isaya 7:1–25</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa41:10\">41:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa51:7-Isa51:8\">51:7–8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa51:12-Isa51:13\">12–13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa54:4\">54:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa57:11\">57:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer10:5\">Yeremia 10:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer30:10\">30:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer46:27-Jer46:28\">46:27–28</a></p>",
